At the end of this week, the student should be able to:
Implement monitoring and obtain reports for cloud service health, security, utilization and performance management.
Examine how security operations centers work with a good grounding on Incident Response methodologies and cyber resilience concepts.
Evaluate current tools and techniques used in security operation centers particularly around logging, packet capture, SIEM, incident tracking and management, threat intelligence, SOAR etc.
Simulate common incident scenarios: email incidents, network incidents, malware incidents.
Use identified tools and techniques to detect, respond, investigate, remediate and report on security incidents

